{"id":317761,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-吉林访民赵桂香被非法劳教，自由后生活/","date":"2013-10-13T05:17:47Z","modified":"2013-10-13T05:17:47Z","title":"维权网 | 吉林访民赵桂香被非法劳教，自由后生活难自理（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员柴民报道）赵桂香是吉林舒兰县人，因两起发生在她家的刑事案件在地方被枉法裁判而到北京上访多年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日中午，赵桂香正在北京的租住房内休息，被舒兰县公安局张姓局长带领七八名便衣警察抓走，回地方后先是行政拘留十天，接着舒兰警方又罗织了莫须有的罪名对她教养一年，在她和办案警察说明他们这是违法行为时，激怒了办案的两位警察，他们骗走了本已经交给赵桂香的教养一年的决定书，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天后，他们又送来一份教养一年零六个月的决定书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>办案的警察对赵桂香说，你去北京各个部门上访已经超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">800</span><span>次了，已经严重地影响了舒兰的形象，今年要开“十八大”，上级要求对你进行绝对的稳控，没有人天天看着你，所以必须教养你。导致赵桂香上访</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">800</span><span>次的原因，是是舒兰县的行政和司法不作为，公权力欠下的孽债让本已冤屈满身的赵桂香来用一年半的牢狱来偿还。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在劳教所，赵桂香原来残疾和多病的身体得不到任何的医治，走出劳教所后连基本生活都难以自理。但赵桂香表示，只要还有一口气，就要和拿老百姓的人权耍闹着玩的强权抗争到底。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qsOUPwMgVAM/UlohO_4uQcI/AAAAAAAApa0/e3HaW5iAPts/s1600/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qsOUPwMgVAM/UlohO_4uQcI/AAAAAAAApa0/e3HaW5iAPts/s320/1.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kAr9fT4hyfI/UlohM2ZkBfI/AAAAAAAApao/-L3AXo3DMbU/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-kAr9fT4hyfI/UlohM2ZkBfI/AAAAAAAApao/-L3AXo3DMbU/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F.jpg\" width=\"198\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-e3bpos_8SS8/UlohMQ8NKOI/AAAAAAAApak/d6mH86B70ik/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+001.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-e3bpos_8SS8/UlohMQ8NKOI/AAAAAAAApak/d6mH86B70ik/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+001.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-kYTK0SV_cC4/UlohUosbzCI/AAAAAAAApa8/mEb8x8qFlyg/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+002.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-kYTK0SV_cC4/UlohUosbzCI/AAAAAAAApa8/mEb8x8qFlyg/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+002.jpg\" width=\"220\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-gBNpbdPmFBo/UlohW-pYLAI/AAAAAAAApbE/5O_6BVFyVOk/s1600/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+003.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-gBNpbdPmFBo/UlohW-pYLAI/AAAAAAAApbE/5O_6BVFyVOk/s320/%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F+003.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}